{
  "date_key": "2026-03-12",
  "date_cn": "2026年03月12日",
  "day_cn": "周四",
  "english": "<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f0fe;border-left:4px solid #1a73e8;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#1a73e8\">时间与金钱（Time, Money, Priorities）</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e3f2fd;border-left:4px solid #0d47a1;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#0d47a1;font-size:15px\">【英文原文】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Hey, you look stressed. What&#x27;s going on?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Dude, I&#x27;m so stretched thin right now. I picked up extra shifts at work, I&#x27;m doing that online certificate course, and my kid&#x27;s got soccer practice every other day. I literally have zero bandwidth left.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Yeah, that sounds brutal. But real talk — is the extra money even worth it? You&#x27;re basically running yourself into the ground.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">I mean, the overtime pay is decent, but honestly, I&#x27;ve been nickel-and-diming myself trying to save up for a house down payment. Like, I&#x27;ll skip lunch, cancel subscriptions, that kind of stuff. But it barely moves the needle.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">I hear you. I used to do the same thing — penny-pinching on every little thing while <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">burning the candle at both ends</span>. Then I realized I was being penny wise, pound foolish. I was saving thirty bucks a month on coffee but spending two hundred on takeout because I was too wiped out to cook.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Ha, that tracks. My wife keeps telling me we need to get our ducks in a row and actually sit down with a budget. But who has the time, right?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Make the time, bro. Seriously. My buddy&#x27;s a financial planner and he said most people don&#x27;t have an income problem — they have a priorities problem. Once we sat down and crunched the numbers, we found like four hundred bucks a month we were just lighting money on fire.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Four hundred? That&#x27;s no joke.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Dead serious. Little stuff adds up — you don&#x27;t even clock it until you see it <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">in black and white</span>. And here&#x27;s the thing: time is money, but money isn&#x27;t time. You can always hustle and earn more cash down the road, but you can&#x27;t buy back Saturday mornings with your kid.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Man, that hit different. I think I&#x27;ve been so caught up in the daily grind that I lost sight of the bigger picture. Maybe it&#x27;s time to stop chasing every dollar and start being more intentional.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Exactly. You don&#x27;t have to go cold turkey on the overtime or anything. Just don&#x27;t let it eat your life. At the end of the day, you gotta put your money where your mouth is — if you say family comes first, then act like it.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">You&#x27;re right. I&#x27;m gonna have that budget talk with my wife this weekend. No more winging it.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">That&#x27;s what&#x27;s up. You got this.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f5e9;border-left:4px solid #1b5e20;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1b5e20;font-size:15px\">【中文翻译】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">嘿，你看起来压力很大。怎么了？</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">兄弟，我现在真的是分身乏术（stretched thin）。我额外加了好几个班，还在上网课考证书，我家孩子隔一天还有足球训练。我真的是一点精力都不剩了（zero bandwidth）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">听着就累。不过说真的（real talk）——多赚那点钱真的值得吗？你这基本上是在把自己往死里整（running yourself into the ground）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">加班费是还行，但说实话，我一直在省小钱攒房子首付（nickel-and-diming）。比如不吃午饭、取消各种订阅之类的。但根本没什么明显效果（barely moves the needle）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">我懂你。我以前也这样——每笔小钱都精打细算，同时还<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">两头烧蜡烛</span>地拼命干。后来我发现自己是捡了芝麻丢了西瓜（penny wise, pound foolish）。一个月省三十块咖啡钱，结果因为太累不想做饭，外卖花了两百块。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">哈，确实是这样。我老婆一直说我们得好好规划一下（get our ducks in a row），坐下来好好做个预算。但谁有那时间呢，对吧？</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">挤出时间来，兄弟。说真的。我一个朋友是理财规划师，他说大多数人不是收入有问题——是优先级有问题。我们坐下来仔细算了一笔账（crunched the numbers），发现每个月有大概四百块就是在白白烧钱（lighting money on fire）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">四百？那可不少。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">真不是开玩笑。小开销积少成多——你根本注意不到（don&#x27;t even clock it），直到你<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">白纸黑字</span>看到它们。而且有一点很重要：时间就是金钱，但金钱买不回时间。你以后总能想办法多赚点钱（down the road），但你买不回跟孩子一起度过的周六早上。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">哥们，这话真的触动到我了。我觉得我被日常的忙碌（daily grind）搞得忘了大局。也许是时候不再追着每一块钱跑了，该更有目的性地生活了。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">就是这个意思。你也不用一下子完全停掉加班（go cold turkey）什么的。只是别让它吞噬你的生活。说到底（at the end of the day），你得言行一致（put your money where your mouth is）——如果你说家人最重要，那就拿出行动来。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">你说得对。这周末我就跟我老婆好好谈谈预算。不能再随便应付了（winging it）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">这才对嘛（That&#x27;s what&#x27;s up）。你行的。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#f3e5f5;border-left:4px solid #4a148c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#4a148c;font-size:15px\">【本日表达列表】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">01.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>stretched thin</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 分身乏术，精力/资源被摊得太薄</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 描述忙到分身乏术、承担太多事情时使用</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">02.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>zero bandwidth</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 完全没有精力/余力去处理更多事</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 科技圈延伸到日常</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 口语中表达&quot;我真的忙不过来了&quot;，从科技术语变成日常口语</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">03.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>nickel-and-diming</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 在小钱上斤斤计较；一点一点地省小钱</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容在小开销上反复节省，或被小额费用一点点掏空</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">04.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>barely moves the needle</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 几乎没有什么明显效果/改变</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 说某件事情的影响微乎其微时使用</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">05.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>penny wise, pound foolish</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 省了小钱却在大钱上犯蠢；捡芝麻丢西瓜</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 英国起源 / 全球通用（美国也常用）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 批评某人在小事上节俭但在大事上浪费</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">06.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>get your ducks in a row</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 做好准备，把事情安排妥当</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 建议别人提前规划、把事情理清楚时使用</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">07.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>crunch the numbers</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 仔细计算/核算数据</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 谈论财务分析、预算计算、做数据工作时使用</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">08.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>lighting money on fire</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 白白烧钱，把钱扔水里</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容极度浪费金钱的行为，口语中带夸张语气</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">09.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>the daily grind</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 日复一日的辛苦工作/忙碌生活</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 描述单调重复的上班生活或日常奔波</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">10.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>put your money where your mouth is</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 说到做到，用行动证明你说的话</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 挑战别人不要光说不练，要拿出实际行动</span></td></tr></table>",
  "beauty": "<div style=\"background:#fce4ec;border-left:4px solid #e91e8c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#c2185b;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#c2185b\">唇妆色号 💋</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">一、棱橄榄皮选唇色的核心逻辑</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">橄榄皮的底色中带有绿调/黄调，这意味着：</p>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>✅ <strong>暖棕、砖红、焦糖、脏橘、暖豆沙</strong>能与肤色和谐融合，显白显气色</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>✅ <strong>带棕调的玫瑰色（干枯玫瑰/枯叶玫瑰）</strong>既日常又高级</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>❌ <strong>冷粉、荧光粉、冷紫、正蓝调红</strong>会放大面部黄气与暗沉，让嘴唇看起来像&quot;浮在脸上&quot;</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; 记住一句口诀：<strong>&quot;宁棕不粉，宁脏不荧。&quot;</strong></p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">二、五大必备色系详解（从日常到进阶）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">1️⃣ 日常通勤 —— 暖调豆沙色</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>色彩特征：粉棕之间、低饱和、带一点灰调</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>效果：柔化面部、素颜感强、不挑场合</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>质地推荐：<strong>丝绒雾面 / 柔雾唇釉</strong>（模糊唇线，圆脸更友好）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">2️⃣ 气色担当 —— 砖红 / 铁锈红</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>色彩特征：红色底调加入棕橘，沉稳不扎眼</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>效果：对橄榄皮<strong>显白效果最强</strong>，秋冬春三季百搭</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>质地推荐：<strong>奶油哑光 / 缎面</strong>（唇部存在感强但不干燥）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">3️⃣ 温柔氛围 —— 干枯玫瑰 / 枯叶玫瑰</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>色彩特征：玫瑰粉底+明显棕灰调，像一朵将谢未谢的玫瑰</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>效果：高级感拉满，比纯粉更安全</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>质地推荐：<strong>水光唇釉薄涂 / 唇泥轻拍</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">4️⃣ 时髦进阶 —— 焦糖脏橘</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>色彩特征：橘棕之间、像太妃糖或烤焦的蜜橘</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>效果：与大地色眼妆天然搭配，打造欧美质感妆</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>质地推荐：<strong>哑光唇膏</strong>（避免水光橘色显村气）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">5️⃣ 气场全开 —— 深棕红 / 酒红棕</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>色彩特征：红+棕+微微酒紫（注意：是暖紫非冷紫）</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>效果：浓妆场合的&quot;王炸色&quot;，适合晚宴/拍照</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>质地推荐：<strong>丝绒哑光</strong>（哑光+深色=利落气场）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">三、圆脸唇妆画法小技巧 ✏️</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">圆脸的目标是让嘴唇成为<strong>视觉纵向焦点</strong>，拉长中庭比例：</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 技巧 | 做法 | 原理 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|------|------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>弱化唇角宽度</strong> | 嘴角两侧留出2-3mm不上色，或用遮瑕轻盖唇角 | 缩窄嘴唇横向宽度 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>强调唇峰</strong> | 用唇线笔在唇峰处微微上提画出V字 | 纵向拉长人中→中庭视觉延展 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>内唇渐变</strong> | 深色集中涂在内唇中央，向外自然晕开 | 嘟唇效果，让五官更立体更聚焦 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| <strong>上下唇比例</strong> | 略微over-line下唇中央1mm | 增加下半脸纵向感 |</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">四、涂法 × 质地 × 持妆的小窍门</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>角质层偏厚的唇部</strong>容易卡纹起皮 → 上妆前用热毛巾敷唇30秒 + 薄涂一层润唇膏等待1分钟后用纸巾轻按吸走油分，再上唇妆</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>毛孔偏大的皮肤</strong>搭配哑光唇妆最平衡 → 全脸雾面+嘴唇也雾面，质感统一</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>持妆叠涂法</strong>：唇膏→纸巾轻抿→散粉隔纸巾按压→再叠涂一层 → 吃饭也不怕</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff9c4;border-left:4px solid #f9a825;padding:12px 16px;margin:14px 0;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#e65100\">💡 <strong>针对你的肤质/脸型：</strong></strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; <strong>棱橄榄皮</strong>：你的皮肤黄调偏重且暗沉，唇色是全脸最快&quot;点亮气色&quot;的一步。<strong>砖红色系</strong>是你的安全牌，<strong>焦糖脏橘</strong>是你的时髦牌，<strong>暖豆沙</strong>是你的日常牌。每次试色时，把口红涂在下颚线附近对比——如果皮肤看起来更亮更干净，就是对的色。</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt;</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; <strong>圆脸</strong>：避免饱和度极高的大红唇铺满全唇（会横向放大嘴唇，显脸更宽）。推荐&quot;<strong>内唇咬唇法</strong>&quot;或&quot;<strong>雾面渐变唇</strong>&quot;，既有颜色又不过度张扬横向宽度。唇峰一定要画清楚，这是圆脸的纵向救星。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e0f7fa;border-left:4px solid #00bcd4;padding:12px 16px;margin:14px 0;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#006064\">🎨 **产品/色号推荐：</strong></div>",
  "research": "<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 1</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Huarong Ma</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Critical Thinking Dispositions of Undergraduate College Students in A Comprehensive University of Mainland China</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">International Journal of Higher Education</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2021</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">4 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">This study was undertaken to assess the critical thinking dispositions of undergraduate college students in a comprehensive university of mainland China and examine the roles of gender and major in the subjects’ critical thinking dispositions. An adapted Chinese version of the California Critical Thinking Dispositions Inventory (CCTDI) was used to survey 534 undergraduate students. Statistics reve…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">该研究聚焦中国大陆本科生的批判性思维倾向评估，与方向一中&quot;assessment&quot;及标准化测评工具（如CCTDI）的使用与效度问题有一定关联，可为反思大规模评估对学生思维能力的衡量方式提供参考。此外，研究揭示中国大学生批判性思维倾向普遍偏弱，这一发现可与方向一中考试反拨效应（washback）的讨论相呼应——即考试文化和教育体制如何塑造或抑制学生的批判性思维发展。但该研究并未直接涉及语言教育、课堂</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.5430/ijhe.v10n6p224\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.5430/ijhe.v10n6p224</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 2</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Zhi Ma</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">From Validity to Equity: Revisiting CET-4 Through Messick, Kane, and Paraskeva’s Frameworks</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">International Journal of Language and Linguistics</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2025</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">0 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">The College English Test Band 4 (CET-4) is a high-stakes, standardised English proficiency assessment widely administered in Chinese universities. Initially developed to evaluate non-English majors’ language competence, it has since evolved into a gatekeeping mechanism that influences graduation eligibility, access to scholarships, postgraduate admissions, and employment opportunities. As English …</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">该论文直接关联<strong>方向一（评估与语言权力）</strong>：它以中国大学英语四级考试（CET-4）为对象，综合运用Messick、Kane及Paraskeva的效度与公平性框架，审视高风险标准化考试作为&quot;守门机制&quot;（gatekeeping mechanism）的角色，涉及assessment validity、washback效应以及考试对多元学习者的公平性问题，与用户关注的epistemic injustice和CDA视角下的语言评估权力批判高度契合。此外，论文对考试如何影响毕业资格、升学及就业机会的分析，也呼应了**方向三（教师与制度）</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.11648/j.ijll.20251303.14\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.11648/j.ijll.20251303.14</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 3</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Andrew Gordon Drybrough</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Conceptualisations of critical thinking in academic writing at a master’s level</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">ERA</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2019</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">0 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Critical thinking is often considered to involve a set of skills required by graduates of higher educational institutions in the UK. However, the conceptualisation of critical thinking by university tutors varies across disciplines and is not always particularly clear. In a UK higher educational context where proportionally increasing numbers of postgraduate students are international, often from …</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">这篇论文探讨高等教育中批判性思维的概念化及其在不同学科和文化背景下的差异，与用户的研究有一定间接关联。首先，它涉及学术评估标准（如导师对批判性思维的界定）如何可能对国际学生构成认知不公（epistemic injustice），与方向一中评估权力和知识合法性的议题相呼应。其次，国际学生（尤其来自不同教育传统的学生）在学术写作中面临的批判性思维期望差异，可延伸至方向一中语言评估的文化霸权与话语分析（CDA）视角，即</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Conceptualisations%20of%20critical%20thinking%20in%20academic%20writing%20at%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20level\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 Google Scholar</a></td></tr></table>\n</div>"
